Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come back and say, "It's impossible, after all,"\Nit would be oh so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen off all kinds of people\Nwho leave on journeys they won't return from...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But... today is the saddest I've ever felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inverted Forest... It's so far above us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the shaft Ozen was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, there is nothing as impartial as death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For all living creatures,\Ndeath is sure to eventually come knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Death is an equalizer - it is an absolute truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is always lingering right beside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, people make the best use\Nof their wits and courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggling... floundering...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they cling to life until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we actually like this unjust and unequal world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, unable to resist, goes down in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make those eyes shine brighter than a torch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The destination we are aiming for is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We squarely lose our way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of the open-mouthed netherworld
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chase the traces of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If an answer can be found now, we don't mind losing it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The echo is still reverberating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we do not part with that voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the yearning stop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Riko and Reg are right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they're somewhere around the Great Fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the result of a calculation I made based on\Nthe number of days it's been and Reg's abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rough Map of the Netherworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a copy of it back when I "borrowed" it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Great Fault"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"A vertical wall spanning more than 4,000 meters"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From there on out,\Nthe strain of ascending becomes more severe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and people start seeing and hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks perfectly smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to descend that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Reg managed to climb it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely there must be a viable route somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Another exit hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's a madokajack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, it's dangerous to stick your head out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only options are to start descending the cliff face,\Nor to brace for the Curse's effect on you and head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other holes nearby...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The spot with the critter droppings sticking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, go ahead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have rather made a delicious meal\Nout of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to fly in the sky or run on walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,weaklings like us are simply picked off and eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaklings have no choice\Nbut to choose the path of the weak, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, hurry and get further inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! This den extends way, way down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quick! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about it bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've descended quite a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I know it was for the sake of pushing forward,\Nbut we totally trashed this den.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be grateful to these little guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks to them we haven't had any trouble\Nfinding food or a place to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And they primarily live on baracocha fruit,\Nso their meat is tender and delicious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these some kind of ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One from a long, long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"A ship"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are still any Relics inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Relics, Relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why is there a ship here in the first place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Any Relics out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there! Relics...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a madokajack's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,lair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I hurl my fists at it, they'll just get chomped on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I just shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you fire it, no matter how you push yourself,\Nyou always faint after around ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a full two hours until you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try leaving a helpless child on her own\Nin the second layer for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just how she'll be torn to shreds and eaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when you really do have to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,go all out to make sure whatever it is\Ndoesn't come after you again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter your opponent or whatever lies in the vicinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when the time comes don't hesitate or show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how madokajacks taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fall asleep before long now that I did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time, you'll be-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it earlier, too, but what the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be a crimson splitjaw...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a wound on its head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the one Reg blasted with his Incinerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I heard they have lairs on the third layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but, this one remembers us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A dead end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Please, little guys! Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna... faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright, Reg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, until I wake up, stay right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, I'll protect you, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to look for some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't leave Reg lying here, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're going now, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry... and worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't press on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here until Reg wakes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the smell of baracochas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be bearing fruit somewhere below me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm close now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the baracochas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, oh where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's the scent coming up from the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This intense scent of baracochas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a neritantan tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm inside the stomach on an amakagame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This scent must be a trap meant to lure neritantans here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get out of here quick\Nor I'll end up getting dissolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell's stuck on me, so they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not baracocha fruit, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is another dead end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it not been two hours yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, come on and wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An opening to the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's there an upward slope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ascend that much, the Curse will-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I can't turn back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg... here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The strain of the depths' third layer:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,headaches, dizziness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...severe nausea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in addition to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,problems with your sense of balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax now, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, won't you head back with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Visual and auditory hallucinations...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough already, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a break. Don't overdo it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great, Riko! Just leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Habo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, let's go back together... back to Orth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're inside a gondola that's heading to Orth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the Curse of the Abyss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is no longer affected by the Curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're about to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the city of Orth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! What about Reg?! Reg's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom of the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Reg's not here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in me even returning to Orth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us were always together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg... Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not together with Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see how hard it is\Nbeing on your own inside the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being protected by you all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are pesky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen taught me how to use this thing, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg! Use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It allowed me to think about lots of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That if I was on my own,\Nthis all would've been impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, it's thanks to you that I was able to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I had Riko with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's the two of us... that we made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The landscape around here has become a lot spikier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our depth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,6,750 meters, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear these spikes are actually eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's a way to make them into a tasty meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, I can see something down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Goblet of Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The glittering waves that float in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bundle them and build a rainbow bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous foothold, a slope we slide on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A signpost of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left hand, with my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Join it, connect us, and let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am always beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, the present, and also the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's walk along without hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pile up multicolored dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will we head toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be together with you, the world will begin to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search for flowers that bloom at the ends of the earth
